# Lingmo OS System Binaries
#
# This directory contains essential system executables.
# These are core components of @DISTRO_NAME@ and
# should NOT be modified or removed.
#
# PATH ordering: /system/bin is the primary system path,
# searched before /vendor/bin and /usr/bin
#
# Contents:
#   - Core system utilities
#   - Init and service managers
#   - Critical system tools
#
# @DISTRO_NAME@ @VERSION@
# Build: @BUILD_VER@
